  "message": "Polish README for launch, remove dist/ from git, add prepublishOnly\n\n- Add CI badge, \"How It Works\" section, benchmark repro instructions\n- Fix gzipped size (51KB \u2192 37KB), benchmark number consistency\n- Tone down marketing language, remove unverified Claude Code claim\n- Remove dist/engine.wasm from git tracking (dist/ already in .gitignore)\n- Add prepublishOnly script so npm publish builds fresh\n- Fix bench box-drawing alignment",
